sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Submit channel creation form
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace
    DB-->>API: Workspace found
    API->>DB: Insert channel
    API->>DB: Add owner as channel member
    DB-->>API: Channel persisted
    API-->>Frontend: 201 Created + channel payload
    Frontend-->>Owner: Refresh channel list
